content.p: Head of Commercialisation, Financial & Business Services George is a senior member of the University of Nottingham Technology Transfer team. He focusses on licensing across the whole University research activity. George's research background is in process engineering before he joined the University Technology Transfer Office in 2008 following a MEDICI Fellowship. George was PraxisUnico 'Newcomer of the year' in 2010 and is a regular speaker on PraxisAuril training courses and conferences. Commercialisation of opportunities arising from research projects. Get in touch: research.innovation@nottingham.ac.uk Jubilee Conference Centre Jubilee Campus Triumph Road Nottingham, NG8 1DH
